# === Ignore all build output for all projects ===
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/docs/

# === Ignore user-specific files ===
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# TFVC-specific folders
$tf/
$tf2/
*.vssscc
*.vspscc
*.scc

# === Ignore VS folders ===
.vs/
.vscode/

# === Ignore NuGet files ===
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
*.nuspec
packages/
project.lock.json
project.assets.json

# === Ignore common temp/log/cache ===
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig
*.cache
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# === Optional: Ignore publish folders if you publish manually ===
**/PublishOutput/
**/ReleaseBuild/
